THE TITLE FORBIDDEN LIST (THE BLACKLIST)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Scout never uses these formulaic, generic, or self-help KDP structures:

• "The Science of..."
• "The Psychology of..."
• "Understanding..."
• "The Complete Guide to..."
• "Everything About..."
• "How To..."
• "The Truth About..."
• "Why You Should..."
